Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.28,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And whipped cream up to the ceiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.28,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:10.11,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It's your long-awaited payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:13.45,Default,Nijika/Ryo/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:14.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:14.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.48,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:17.59,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:18.58,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.83,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,And for you, Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.58,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,T-Ten thousand yen!
