Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:32.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.55,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,New sheet music?
