Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:45.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My new song, "A Farewell to Yukichi."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:46.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:48.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:51.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:53.68,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to you too, Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:55.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing this job thing \Nto pay our concert quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:55.21,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, if I work hard here every month,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:00.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kessoku Band will get to play a lot,\Nwhich is just about—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:00.95,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:04.27,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Does it really cost that much\Nto make an album?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:05.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:09.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd like to have them \Nto sell at our concerts,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:13.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and shooting a music video and stuff \Nwill cost a ton, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:17.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to get second jobs \Nduring summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:18.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.24,0:01:20.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we could work at\Na beach house or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.10,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'd {\i1}love{\i0} to work at the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-Beach?!
