Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.40,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's a no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That would be so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.00,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They won't lend to minors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:33.73,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But perhaps, deeper in the \Ninternet's shadier corners...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:36.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to sell my liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:37.45,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.23,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-sure I could get a loan \Nusing my guitar as collateral,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:43.74,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,s-so please don't make me get another job!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:47.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't make me work at \Nthe beach or an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:49.70,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I wrote the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.37,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Is it just me, or is it really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.37,0:02:00.30,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.68,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,When I read Bocchi's lyrics, \Nit just came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,All the hard work paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.92,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That's my girl. There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:13.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai! I'm working hard, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten so good at guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:18.50,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:20.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:22.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me chin rubs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.56,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,My dream might just come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.86,0:02:28.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask Sis to let us hold \Nour concert here next month!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:34.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't asked her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.27,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She let us in right away last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:39.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.76,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not putting you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:45.85,Default,Hitori/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.46,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked dark, cramped spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:04.83,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd bury my face deep in my hood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.21,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes resented the heartless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.96,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,but yearned for love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.60,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked being soaked by the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.97,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,because my face looked better clouded over
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.61,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be afraid of the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:25.44,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,while waiting for the sky to burst
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:32.40,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum through the light's distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.82,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make thunder roar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:42.62,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum beyond the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.75,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:52.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum in a harmonizing quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.80,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cause a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:02.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum in a lamenting forte
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:07.56,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.86,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H178BDF&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(238.5,132.5)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.86,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H178BDF&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(416.5,255)}#05 Flightless Fish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.98,BText,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\b0\pos(437,107)}Potential August Bands\N\N• Macaroni Pencil\N\N• Yukiguni with Tunnel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:21.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But why? We just finished our original song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.17,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I care about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This feels super awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We can even pay our quota \Nif we don't bring in customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.50,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.21,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It's about your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But you let us play last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.44,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I made an exception so you \Ncould make a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,"Make a memory"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:45.30,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I'd make you play first to apply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.68,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:52.58,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I can't have a repeat \Nof that awful May performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Can't have a repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:59.57,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Just stick with it as a hobby or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.28,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You got more to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.91,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even sleep without \Nstuffed animals to cuddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ijichi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.71,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,That was a weird parting shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.21,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Would the stuffed animals in question
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.17,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,be this beat-up panda and rabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.17,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.52,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Delete that image! Immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? We have to go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.68,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like it's too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.64,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:40.72,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:41.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:54.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious when you're sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:06:00.27,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to rush out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't have to be such \Na jerk about it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:08.05,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.86,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.74,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-Manager... said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.29,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.90,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, breathe first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:25.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.04,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:31.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... The manager told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.33,BText,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\b0\pos(426.5,108.5)}Potential August Bands\N\N• Macaroni Pencil\N\N• Yukiguni with Tunnel\N\N\N\N\N\N• Inoue brothers\N\N\N\N\N• Ryokuoushoku Yasai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.33,BText,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\b0\pos(426.5,300)\alpha&HFF&\t(654,696,\alpha&H00&)}• {\alpha&HFF&\t(780,821,\alpha&H00&)}Ke{\alpha&HFF&\t(905,946,\alpha&H00&)}s{\alpha&HFF&\t(1072,1113,\alpha&H00&)}so{\alpha&HFF&\t(1197,1238,\alpha&H00&)}ku {\alpha&HFF&\t(1322,1363,\alpha&H00&)}Ba{\alpha&HFF&\t(1447,1489,\alpha&H00&)}n{\alpha&HFF&\t(1614,1655,\alpha&H00&)}d
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.33,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Nijika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.20,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,If she wants to perform, \Nshe needs to audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:40.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch the performances \Nnext Saturday and decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:41.13,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.13,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm desperately attempting \Nto show obedience!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:49.73,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You should probably go after them \Nbefore you lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:50.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.76,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,When a dog rolls over to show its belly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,some believe that's not \Na show of submission,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:06:59.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,but a show of aggression.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-senpai knows so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.82,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,An audition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.49,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And if we pass, she'll let us perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why didn't she just \Nsay so to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That sister of mine is so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.81,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But that means we just have to work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:23.22,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:25.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.08,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You've got that "those two are the \Nbiggest problem" look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:29.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Erk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.13,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(196,1)\c&H5626E0&\3c&HF3F8FC&\bord2\pos(193.5,193)}Erk
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:33.84,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We'll record your parts in advance, \Nso just practice miming along!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.39,Default,Hitori/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No! No air guitars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.52,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We've only got a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.44,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push them so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:43.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they suck, the passion \Nwill come through if they try!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:44.80,Default,Hitori/Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We suck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.05,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:49.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're really both way \Nbetter than you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:50.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:52.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, back me up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:54.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't turn into a pipe shut-in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.65,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry for my momentary arrogance \Nover my success in writing lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:03.17,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2\fnComic Sans MS\c&H181B18&\bord2.5\3c&HFCFEFC&\clip(m 255 0 l 256 17 281 87 309 123 0 147 0 0)\move(650,80,-325,80)}sorry for my momentary arrogance over my success in writing lyrics those with uncontrollable arrogance deserve a life inside a dark dank pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.54,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's The Sound of Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Those with uncontrollable arrogance \Ndeserve a life inside a dark, dank pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:04.31,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.73,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,They think she isn't good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.67,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:10.12,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,At least when I heard her at school before,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:13.30,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,even I could tell as a novice\Nthat she's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.64,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, come out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.69,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Please just come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.22,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I could remove myself \Nfrom your memory, I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.22,DefaultItalics,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Was that just dumb luck before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:22.34,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So long as the rhythm section's strong, \Nit'll probably work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:24.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:29.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they need to see us \Nall playing on Ryo's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.19,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what {\i1}do{\i0} they need to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:36.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... enthusiasm? Growth as a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.19,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:48.42,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,For practicing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.67,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.97,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But shouldn't we practice in a classroom \Ninstead of this dreary place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.96,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, w-well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.75,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to practice with \Nall those judging eyes asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,"What's a cool girl like Kita \Ndoing with that loser?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:06.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:10.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to bother people \Nby playing in a classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.61,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're so considerate, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She always assumes my motivations are pure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:17.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gotoh-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:22.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I think we just need to show
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.20,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,that we've grown as a band—\Nin other words, how hard we've been working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:28.33,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:31.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,When the time comes, I want to \Nbe able to say I gave it my all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and that I don't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:38.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So please stick with me until \Nthe day of the audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:40.52,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.34,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm the one who's h-happy to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:10:00.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,"V-Visually showing our growth \Nas a band"... Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,More of Ryo's mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.32,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking, smoking, dalliances with women,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.39,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and the mop-top hairstyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.43,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It all equals "band."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're laying it on a little thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And no smoking or drinking \Nuntil you're twenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.55,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone say, "mop-top"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:16.21,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Gotten it out of your system?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:21.12,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We've got an opening for \N"uneven bangs that hide one eye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.23,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and a perpetually annoyed expression."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I c-can't have dalliances with women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.57,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I d-don't think any women \Nwould want to dally with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:34.82,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Stand in front of VillePan in Shimo-Kitazawa, \Nwearing your guitar and looking listless,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:40.02,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and someone'll come up to you \Nsooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:41.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop misinforming her with \Nyour subjective experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.83,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But growth isn't always visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.80,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And the criteria is quite vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's very clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.97,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to convince Sis to take us on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Practice is the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.30,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:02.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get what Ryo-san's saying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:13.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to know exactly \Nwhat "growth" means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.36,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:18.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's quite the same \Nas effort put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My life as of late has been a whirlwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I started working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've gained the ability to occasionally \Nlook others in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:33.66,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Your finger's looking better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:39.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think that's the same thing \Nas growing as a band.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've just evolved past the \Nwater flea or euglena stage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:45.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and now stand at the starting line \Nof basic humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I thought finally starting \Nthe band I dreamed about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:52.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,would be growth in itself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:01.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:02.74,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Get a good night's rest\Nfor the audition tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.71,0:12:07.49,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.13,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.51,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't mean to startle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.85,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:29.31,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Cola, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.45,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:39.69,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:44.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if I forced you to go along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:51.30,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you kind of just got roped into \Njoining Kessoku Band from the start, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,you'd been wanting \Nto be part of a band,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:03.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but I never actually asked you what \Nkind of band you wanted to be in,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:08.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,or what your reasons were \Nfor playing in this band now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:14.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Should I tell her I started because \NI wanted people going crazy for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's got their own reasons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like performing live \Nis the only way to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:26.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You can always post videos and stuff nowadays\Nif what you want is to get your sound out there.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.57,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
