Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:41.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,See... I've got this kind of goal. \NA dream, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:44.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So I can get a little fired up \Nwithout realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:49.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So... I worry I might have dragged you \Ninto this against your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.06,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's n-n-not against my will at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.39,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you wanted a band...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's to get famous and perform \Nat the Budokan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,My real dream is actually a little past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:15.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't tell you just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.76,0:14:17.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.09,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,276)\fsp4\c&HFCFEFF&}Day of the Audition
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:40.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all night thinking about my reason
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:43.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,for playing in this band now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:55.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to play our song, \N"Guitar, Solitude, and the Blue Planet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I do still want to become popular
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and have everyone go crazy for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:09.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But now... it's not just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's the four of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.94,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A sudden evening shower falls
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:30.88,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And yeah, it figures, \NI don't have an umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:34.95,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares how the sky's feeling, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.08,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,When it's time for the seasons to change
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never figured out what \Nit means to have "growth."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.83,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What are you supposed to wear? Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:44.79,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Spring and fall... yeah, where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.87,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, what I want
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,is to stay with this band and \Nhave people go crazy for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:49.80,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The pressure of information, suffocating
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.36,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A spiral of vertigo
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make Nijika-chan's \Nactual dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.76,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know where I am
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:16:00.89,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear myself breathing \Nso loud, so loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:59.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,So... I can't afford to blow this audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:06.23,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I can't hear the \Nsounds of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:05.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the band to end just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.35,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough, not enough, \NNo one knows I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:15.52,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I screamed when I couldn't \Nmake a scribble of a sound
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:20.41,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I supposed to show "just who I am" to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:25.25,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm singing just like the fool I am
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:28.55,Songs_Insert,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's lay it all out to the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:59.78,DefaultTop,Hitori/Ryo/Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:15.97,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:19.52,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I'd like to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.94,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Drums, you're too tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.98,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Guitars, you're both looking down too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.37,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Bass, you're too holed up \Nin your own little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:35.78,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Still... I think I know what \Nkind of band you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you... for the feedback.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.33,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.37,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.84,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, I learned what \Nkind of band you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.54,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,This is the part where you cheer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.34,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's saying you passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:57.43,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said! You passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you're so misleading!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:07.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You mean... we did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:11.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She says we passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.69,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We really did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:15.87,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.39,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo, did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:17.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:18.89,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:23.20,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been long, but Bocchi-chan's \Nplaying is so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:21.33,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You were really incredible there, Gotoh-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, Kita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:28.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?
