Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:47.48,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\pos(315,121)\c&HFCFCFA&\3c&H1D251D&\bord2.5\b0}One Moment, Please
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:47.48,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnImpact\fs14\pos(370,228)\b0}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:37.01,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(898,1021)\fs12\bord1\pos(560,333.5)}Toyama Prefecture\NKurobe Dam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:42.55,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(982,1514)\fs12\bord1\pos(560,333.5)}Iwate Prefecture\NYuda Dam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:47.48,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1359,1)\fs12\bord1\pos(80,333.5)}Nagano Prefecture\NMisogawa Dam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.45,DefaultItalicsTop,Nijika/Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Did we just imagine that performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Need a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:51.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:54.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Too many new things at once put \Nmy stomach acid into overdrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.63,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Of course your stomach's \Nfreaked out a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe we passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.67,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.32,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've even thought up our next song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's my senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, easy to say after it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:15.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't I clean the floor first?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:17.96,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She really is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:22.60,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,But she's so inexperienced \Nplaying with a team
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:25.97,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,that her lack of self-confidence \Nholds her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.98,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She could grow even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:38.00,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.45,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Has the manager been making \Neye contact with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.97,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,To give her confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.60,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,she needs to know someone out there \Nacknowledges her talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:55.63,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking at me! Is she mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Because I let victory make me arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.05,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.55,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I see you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:11.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's watching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:13.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.52,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.11,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.86,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Admit it. You liked them from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:28.60,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you've been keeping a window open \Nin the concert schedule for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.25,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Why tease them like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.77,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't teasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I just didn't want to put them on \Nuntil they were ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:39.20,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,But while they're still \Nrough around the edges,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.26,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I think they've got something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:46.64,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,As her sister, I need to be hard on her \Nto make sure her band grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:50.94,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what they call a sister complex?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.12,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,One more word about that, and you're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:54.14,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:59.64,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's work even harder to level up \Nour band in the lead-up to the concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.03,Default,Hitori/Kita/Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:04.00,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi, I'm looking forward \Nto the new lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:07.99,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this getting exciting, Gotoh-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:09.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right! It's not over at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:17.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, Kessoku Band's journey \Nis just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:22.34,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now, since the ticket quota is twenty at \N1,500 yen each, that means we each sell five!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Five-ticket quota...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Five-ticket quota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Five tickets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Five-ticket quota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.45,DefaultItalics,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's inscribing\Nher name into rock history...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.74,DefaultItalics,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cook some red rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:40.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.82,DefaultItalics,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:44.40,DefaultItalics,Jimihen,0000,0000,0000,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.44,DefaultItalicsTop,Naoki/Michiyo/Futari/Jimihen,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Red rice! Awesome! Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Father, mother, sister, dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.09,DefaultItalicsTop,Naoki/Michiyo/Futari/Jimihen,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Red rice! Awesome! Woof!
