Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:51.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Father, mother, sister, dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:54.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... I h-have one left over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:56.73,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san is so happy, she's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:59.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We have to put on a great concert together!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.00,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:04.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's really over this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:21.47,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep, with big problems \Nweighing down on me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:32.13,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you can't beat that feeling \Nof being loved, it's true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.13,0:22:41.81,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I awaken from cold dreams, \Nmy body feels numb
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:50.55,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shine so brightly, \Nit could make me a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:55.43,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to take that step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:23:03.15,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Though there's nothing certain about it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:10.28,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It carries my childish heart into tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:14.65,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to blast out the thoughts \Nrattling around in my brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:17.23,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,And live, to its fullest, a life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:22.21,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been taking advances on for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.72,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also love the days I spend \Nlying around, doing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:27.34,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,So I know I'm going to go see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:33.14,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it all disappears some day
